## ğŸ—ºï¸ Roadmap

### Current Release: v0.1.41 (Oct 14, 2025)

**Latest Features**:
- âœ… **API Caching Layer**: DuckDB-based caching with 42 cached tool functions across 9 data sources
- âœ… **Cache Warming**: Pre-populate cache with `/cache warm` (23 common queries: indices, FAANG+, treasury, GDP/CPI)
- âœ… **Cache Management**: `/cache` (statistics), `/cache clear` (invalidate), intelligent TTL per source
- âœ… **Performance Boost**: Up to 75% hit rates on repeated queries, instant responses from cache
- âœ… **Smart Caching**: Real-time data (60s TTL), fundamentals (1h), economic indicators (24h)

**Previous Release** (v0.1.40):
- âœ… **`/protect` Workflow**: Portfolio hedging with Risk Shield + Hedge Smith collaboration
- âœ… **Worker-based Workflows**: Non-blocking execution for responsive TUI

### Recent Releases

**v0.1.39** (Oct 14, 2025):
- âœ… **`/optimize-tax` Workflow**: Tax-loss harvesting with replacement strategies (Tax Scout + Hedge Smith)
- âœ… **Worker-based Workflows**: Non-blocking execution for all multi-agent workflows

**v0.1.38** (Oct 14, 2025):
- âœ… **ESC Cancellation**: Cancel long-running agent operations anytime
- âœ… **Non-blocking TUI**: Scroll and interact while agents work
- âœ… **Worker-based Execution**: Textual worker pattern for responsive UI
- âœ… **Graceful Stream Cleanup**: Proper async stream handling on cancellation

**v0.1.37** (Oct 12, 2025):
- âœ… **Extended `/analyze` Workflow**: 5-agent comprehensive analysis (Quill + News Sentry + Macro Lens + Risk Shield + Tax Scout)
- âœ… **`/discover` Workflow**: Systematic idea generation (Screen Forge + Quill + Risk Shield)
- âœ… **Progressive Streaming**: Real-time display of sub-agent tool calls
- âœ… **State Accumulation**: Each agent receives context from previous agents

**v0.1.36** (Oct 11, 2025):
- âœ… **Automatic Intent-Based Routing**: No more manual agent switchingâ€”just ask naturally
- âœ… **Router Agent**: LangGraph tool-calling supervisor coordinating 10 specialist agents
- âœ… **Enhanced Transparency**: Watch router analyze intent and select appropriate agents
- âœ… **Backward Compatible**: All `/command` syntax still works for power users

**v0.1.35** (Oct 10, 2025):
- âœ… **Hedge Smith Agent**: Options strategies (collars, covered calls, puts), Greeks analysis

**v0.1.34** (Oct 9, 2025):
- âœ… **Tax Scout Agent**: Tax-loss harvesting, wash-sale compliance, year-end planning

